description: A Fan failure has been detected

Summary.eval: ($v1==1 && $v2==1 && $v3==1 && $v4==1 && $v5==1 && $v6==1) ? 'Fan tray is fully operational' : (($v1==2 && $v2==2 && $v3==2 && $v4==2 && $v5==2 && $v6==2) ? 'Fan tray in failure condition (all fan units failed)' : (($v1==2) ? 'Fan unit 1 failed' : (($v2==2) ? 'Fan unit 2 failed' : (($v3==2) ? 'Fan unit 3 failed' : (($v4==2) ? 'Fan unit 4 failed' : (($v5==2) ? 'Fan unit 5 failed' : 'Fan unit 6 failed'))))))
